snippet.title: Viva Piñata: Party Animals E3 2007 Trailer
snippet.description:
Happy 200 Subscribers at the time of this upload!
Sourced from the demo of Viva Piñata: Party Animals as seen on the Xbox Live Marketplace and probably a couple of demo discs seen in official Xbox magazines. Uprezed from 1280x720 to 2560x1440 in Handbrake.
